snippet.title: Trick Shot 2 - Out now
snippet.description:
Simply get the ball in the box, how hard can it be?

Trick Shot 2 is the followup to the award winning original, bringing new levels a fully featured level creator and infinite possibilities.

Download on the App Store here:

https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/trick-shot-2/id1315443633?ls=1&mt=8

Twitter: https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/

Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/trickshotapp/
